parameters.content:
## ðŸ¤– Nano ðŸŒ / Seedream -> 4k Video
## | [Created by Chase AI](https://www.skool.com/chase-ai)

## How it Works
### - Trigger inside Airtable
### - Grabs first + last frame images for each scene
### - Images send to Fal.AI for video creation
### - Scenes uploaded to Airtable, await approval
### - Once approved, videos are stiched + upscaled
### - Clips are stitched together via ffmpeg
### - Final video upscaled via Topaz
### - Video uploaded to Airtable

## APIs Needed
### - [Airtable](https://docs.n8n.io/integrations/builtin/credentials/airtable/?utm_source=n8n_app&utm_medium=credential_settings&utm_campaign=create_new_credentials_modal)
### - Fal.ai

## Resources
### - [Airtable Template](https://airtable.com/appc6csgkqrLMZWd4/shrpzijGtV9bVoxq6) (Copy the base + update webhook)
### - [Nano Banana](https://aistudio.google.com/prompts/new_chat) (Free)
### - [Seed Dream](https://fal.ai/models/fal-ai/bytedance/seedream/v4/edit) ($0.03 / image)
### - [Minimax](https://fal.ai/models/fal-ai/minimax/hailuo-02/pro/image-to-video) ($0.08 / second)
### - [FFMPEG](https://fal.ai/models/fal-ai/ffmpeg-api/merge-videos) ($0.0002 / second)
### - [Topaz](https://fal.ai/models/fal-ai/topaz/upscale/video) ($0.033 / second)

## Cost per 6s 4k Upscaled Video "Scene"
### ~ $0.68 = $0.48 (Video) + $0.20 (Upscale)

fields.Title: phone
fields.Video Prompt: Cinematic assembly sequence starting with iPhone components scattered and disassembled on white background. Camera holds wide shot showing all parts laid out precisely. Begin reverse-engineering animation where individual components smoothly float and rotate into position - screws threading themselves, circuit boards sliding into place, camera modules clicking in, frame pieces connecting seamlessly. Parts move with fluid mechanical precision, guided by invisible magnetic forces. As the final exterior shell closes and the Apple logo appears, the phone gently settles onto the white surface. Screen illuminates with startup sequence, then transitions to show Google Maps with navigation interface displaying street map, location pins, and 'Turn left onto Elm Street, 15 min' direction. Camera slowly pushes in on the completed device. Professional product photography lighting throughout

fields.Title: phone
fields.Video Prompt: Dynamic transformation starting with iPhone displaying flat 2D Google Maps interface in portrait orientation on white background. Camera holds steady as the map content begins to come alive - street lines start to glow and pulse with subtle animation. Buildings and city blocks begin to extrude upward from the flat screen surface, rising into white 3D geometric forms that break the plane of the display. The phone simultaneously rotates to a dynamic angled perspective as the map transforms from flat to dimensional. 3D buildings continue growing taller, creating depth and realistic urban topology. Streets maintain their blue and yellow color routing while gaining elevation changes. The transformation emphasizes the 'immersive 3D' experience as text 'Google Maps. Now in immersive 3D, right on your screen.' appears elegantly beside the device.
